    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Bonus Action, you can reach into your Alchemist's Satchel and pull out a vial of vibrant healing liquid. A creature of your choice can drink it as an Bonus Action to allow them to expend a number of Hit Die up to your Proficiency Bonus to regain Hit Points. The creature must be within your reach to be given the vial. You can drink the vial as part of the same Bonus Action used to pull the vial out. Once consumed the vial then disappears. If not used, the vial and its contents disappear after 1 hour. While the vial exists, you cannot use this formula.</p>",
